# imgorient

## Usage
```
imgorient <img_path>
```

## Example

### Test image

<img src="./img/syokki_hashi_man.png" width="300">

### command
```
imgorient ./img/syokki_hashi_man.png
```
### output
```
angle: 47.325422492344984
intensity: 0.6059812726967501
```

